channel.description:
Hello, i'm going to keep this short and sweet. I'm looking for a partner to work on a RuneScape framework with. I'm open to the networking system and overall design and would just like a second set of hands to work on this with me. If your interested you can fill out this application and then we'll go from there. I haven't started this project yet but I've written many server skeletons and applications in the past. We'll use Drop Box for the time being.
